SYNTHESIZE SAVE

@include.the.synthesize.command

@include.the.save.option

USAGE: spx synthesize [...] --save FILENAME

EXAMPLES

  spx synthesize --files *.txt --save test1.job
  spx synthesize --files *.txt;*.ssml --audio output {id}.wav --save test2.job
  spx synthesize --files @URLs.txt --output zip output.zip --save test3.job

  spx synthesize @test3.job

  spx synthesize --foreach file;audio.output in @filelist.txt --save test4.job
  spx synthesize @test4.job

SEE ALSO

  spx help synthesize
  spx help synthesize files
  spx help synthesize foreach
